headline: Leidos enhancing information sharing, decision making across U.S. security agencies
summary: Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) is modernizing the IT operations of the Compartmented Enterprise Services Office (CESO) within the Defense Information Systems Agency (DISA) to enable more efficient information sharing across the Department of War (DoW) and intelligence community.
